{"tid":533133,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京阪神5月10天行程求指點","createTime":"2018-01-18T13:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T13:33:27.000Z","uid":24667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0611734d329d0afe83c3665bd2434395412ff4","tid":533133,"uid":24667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊5月第一次去京阪神麻煩大家指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n京都會住火車站附近<br />\n大阪就梅田<br />\n<br />\n17/5 (京都) 4:20 pm 落機(會買ICOCA＆HARUKA套票) 去到京都check in 附近行下 (京都火車站+京都塔)<br />\n18/5 (京都) 伏見+宇治 <br />\n19/5 (京都) 八坂神社&gt;石塀小路&gt;高台寺&gt;二三年坂&gt;清水坂&gt;清水寺<br />\n20/5  (京都) 嵐山 &gt; 金閣寺 (睇緊搭唔搭小火車,好似5月冇咩睇咁) <br />\n21/5 (京都) 銀閣寺&gt;永觀堂&gt;南禪寺&gt;平安神宮&gt;二條城 6:00pm 搭車去大阪+check in+ 晚餐<br />\n22/5 (大阪)大阪火車站&gt;大阪城&gt;新世界  &gt;通天閣&gt;日本橋 &gt;黑門市場 &gt;晚餐北極星蛋包飯 &gt;梅田夜景 <br />\n23/5 奈良 一日遊<br />\n24/5 (大阪) USJ<br />\n25/5 (大阪)海遊館&rarr;天保山摩天輪&rarr;心齋橋&rarr;道頓堀 (呢日諗緊轉唔轉做神戶1日遊)<br />\n26/5 (大阪) 11:00 check out 周圍買下野5點去機場搭飛機番香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212b53dd7bd59118044d4c9617a80480fd1c4bf2","tid":533133,"uid":24667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39065fc3ecd51bd74e7600f84b057c3fef70e9f4","tid":533133,"uid":1587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:19:49.000Z","msg":"支持行神戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8048726ad6d88ab58c8cc4939c604210